Interface Contribution

  • All Superinterfaces:
    ElementLink, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, URNmodelElement
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ContributionImpl

    public interface Contribution
extends URNmodelElement, ElementLink
    A representation of the model object 'Contribution'.

    The following features are supported:

    • Name
    • Long Name
    • Dest
    • Correlation
    • Contribution
    • Quantitative Contribution
